{"id":836423511,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"7 months, 3 weeks","timestamp":1667524122,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"4 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/836423511/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Reverse Vowels of a String","memory":"45.2 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public String reverseVowels(String s) {\n        char[] array = s.toCharArray();\n        int left = 0, right = array.length - 1;\n\n\n        while (left < right) {\n            if (!isVowel(array[left])) {\n                left++;\n            } else if (!isVowel(array[right])) {\n                right--;\n            } else {\n                swap(array, left, right);\n                left++;\n                right--;\n            }\n        }\n        return String.valueOf(array);\n    }\n\n    private boolean isVowel(char c) {\n        return c == 'a' || c == 'e' || c == 'i' || c == 'o' || c == 'u' || c == 'A' || c == 'E' || c == 'I' || c == 'O' || c == 'U';\n    }\n\n    private void swap(char[] array, int i, int j) {\n        char temp = array[i];\n        array[i] = array[j];\n        array[j] = temp;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"reverse-vowels-of-a-string","has_notes":false}
